198
00:08:18,207 --> 00:08:19,208
Jenny,

199
00:08:22,044 --> 00:08:22,878
Sam,

200
00:08:25,631 --> 00:08:26,

201
00:08:25,631 --> 00:08:26,507
e Emma.

202
00:08:26,965 --> 00:08:30,135
♪ (Letra incompreensível)
eu faria... ♪

